edge_1: Abandoned by her owner in the streets of London, Victoria is rescued and introduced to a group of alley cats known as the Jellicles who prepare her for the annual Jellicle Ball.
edge_2: The Jellicles, reunited with their kidnapped brethren, and perched on a lion statue, watch Grizabella ascend as the morning sun appears above the horizon.

edge_1: Old Deuteronomy witnesses their quiet camaraderie and assures Victoria that she can become a Jellicle herself in time.
edge_2: Old Deuteronomy asks Mr. Mistoffelees to use his powers to conjure Old Deuteronomy back, and he eventually succeeds in doing so.
